<pb n="0237a" id="I01.0089.0237a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 89</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>舜禪師等百餘人造像記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a01"/><p id="pI01p0237a0101">□邑主禪師舜　象主劉□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a02"/>□夫<note n="0237001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30601;＝明【史】</note><app n="0237001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30601;</rdg></app><app source="0237001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30601;</rdg></app>萬象。仰之誰得其□。
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a03"/>攸攸<note n="0237002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31089;＝兆【史】</note><app n="0237002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">兆</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31089;</rdg></app>庶。俯之熟測其際。唯大
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a04"/>□靈尊。威神&CB07099;量。籠括空有。獨
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a05"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">在</unclear>環中。演三乘於苦海。為眾生
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a06"/>之樑棟。隨六道之去來。示北首
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a07"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">於</unclear>雙林。其有舜禪師者。閑居味
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a08"/>□。捨苦<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">樂</unclear>於一心。<note n="0237003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">豦＝據【史】</note><app n="0237003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">據</lem><rdg wit="【原】">豦</rdg></app>披&CB07099;<note n="0237004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31090;＝罦【史】</note><app n="0237004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">罦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31090;</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a09"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">方</unclear>便以開導。欲使未曾有法。給
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a10"/>□荼心。&CB07099;緣之慈。引其鄙意。復
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a11"/>有<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">劉</unclear>洪安。劉專。劉嶠常。劉獻伯。
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a12"/>□□□。劉黑等。性與天道。直置
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a13"/>□□□慍不改其容。榮辱何關
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a14"/>在□。□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">鷲</unclear>鸑之長歎。慨羅預之
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a15"/>見<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">損</unclear>。傷慧日□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">傳</unclear>。痛金棺於
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a16"/>長夜。遂率宗門一百餘人。共興
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a17"/>□攝之心。俱起□天之念。欲令
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a18"/>甘露久光。金河□盡。法幢更暉。
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a19"/>慧炬復照。即敬造<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">西</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">方</unclear><note n="0237005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31091;＝阿【史】</note><app n="0237005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">阿</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31091;</rdg></app><note n="0237006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02793;＝彌【史】</note><app n="0237006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02793;</rdg></app>陀
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a20"/>像。并觀音。大勢。白毫宛轉。與五
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a21"/>山如爭隆。青目分明。共四海如
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a22"/><note n="0237007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB15137;＝競【史】</note><app n="0237007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">競</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB15137;</rdg></app>朗。一一相好。不得兼二以觀
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a23"/>之。頌德弗閑。豈復更□於餘偈。
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a24"/>將知巍巍難量。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">猶</unclear>山玉之對川
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a25"/>長。唐唐易睹。若<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">二</unclear>日之現華池。
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a26"/>昔不傾不動。由□木如往生。不
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a27"/>穢不濁。因聚沙之微業。況功同
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a28"/>□石。神等育王。豈使催時之獸
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a29"/>虛馳如往返。減<note n="0237008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08832;＝算【史】</note><app n="0237008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">算</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08832;</rdg></app>之禽空驟於
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a30"/>去來。乃為頌曰。　　二儀覆載。
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a31"/>万品有緣。受業各異。感果相牽。
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a32"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">御</unclear>龍奕世。英倫比肩。<note n="0237009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30338;＝刻【史】</note><app n="0237009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">刻</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30338;</rdg></app>作能仁。
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a33"/>相好殊妍。&CB00150;若畫石。猶月昇天
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a34"/>□□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">飾</unclear>。沾及&CB07099;邊。四恩九居。
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a35"/>□茲福田。慈氏三會。上首俱前。
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a36"/>□之金石。□□斯年。
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a37"/>　大齊武<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">平</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">元</unclear>年歲在攝提星
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a38"/>　□□月□寶鐘經始故記之
<lb ed="C I" n="0237a39"/>　　　　　　大施主劉□□</p>
